{"tid":1498544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何式凝：網民說我累到天水圍超過80名示威者被拘捕慘被黑警虐待 根本是抹黑、批鬥和人格謀殺 我不會認錯","createTime":"2019-08-23T12:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T06:48:34.000Z","uid":252492,"like":6,"dislike":539,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8691a485a8b95ac652c95c941b8c895b62fd61","tid":1498544,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"Ho Sik Ying<br />\nAugust 20 at 2:00 AM &middot; <br />\n<br />\n「從自由西說起：亂世中談愛慾與民主」<br />\n<br />\n感謝友好過去十多天給我的支持。雖不知道何時我才可從被抹黑、批鬥和人格謀殺中䆁放出來，8月25日（星期天），Women&rsquo;s Festival 的講座「亂世中的愛慾和民主」將如期舉行。我會回顧這件事，說說我條仔、我個 Ex 和我親近的人怎樣和我渡過艱難的日子，讓我重新理解情和愛的意義。<br />\n<br />\n這事之後，我們報稱關心性 / 別公義和親密關係的人又可以怎樣面對大家？Carmen 和 Pamela 會和我一起探討如何。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157133206415306&amp;id=664820305&amp;anchor_composer=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157133206415306%26id%3D664820305%26anchor_composer%3Dfalse&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=57f448be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157133206415306&amp;id=664820305&amp;anchor_composer=false</a>"},{"pid":"ed64cb2ddfc087582596252f0560b91b1fe54afd","tid":1498544,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b0b95fd77c39334e7ea2418981d4b7cfb18546","tid":1498544,"uid":114459,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"左膠必須死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cbeabbfb30e7ea5ec33e31a443652f59cfa4d6","tid":1498544,"uid":216817,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aea0e9414edffe16568e7ca9f099f244d9e25587","tid":1498544,"uid":72859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08